test.scenarios('vlt')

test.lint()

test.passes()
```
## LHS mismatch internal error

Error message:
```cpp
%Error: Internal Error: t/t_dfg_peephole_bug.v:13:19: ../V3DfgPeephole.cpp:955: Mismatched LHS width
   13 |    assign o = arr | i + 1;
      |                   ^
                        ... See the manual at https://verilator.org/verilator_doc.html for more assistance.
```

Failing test:
```sv
// DESCRIPTION: Verilator: Verilog Test module
//
// This file ONLY is placed under the Creative Commons Public Domain, for
// any use, without warranty, 2024 by Antmicro.
// SPDX-License-Identifier: CC0-1.0

module t(
   input [1:0] i,
   output [1:0] o
   );

   wire [1:0] arr [1:0];
   assign o = arr | i + 1;
endmodule
```

Test runner code the same as above.
